<refsect2 id="oil-rand-s32" role="macro">
<title>oil_rand_s32()</title>
<indexterm zone="oil-rand-s32"><primary sortas="oil_rand_s32">oil_rand_s32</primary></indexterm><programlisting>#define oil_rand_s32() ((rand()&amp;0xffff)&lt;&lt;16 | (rand()&amp;0xffff))
</programlisting>
<para>
Evaluates to a random integer in the range [-(1&lt;&lt;31), (1&lt;&lt;31)-1].</para>
<para>
</para></refsect2>
<refsect2 id="oil-rand-s16" role="macro">
<title>oil_rand_s16()</title>
<indexterm zone="oil-rand-s16"><primary sortas="oil_rand_s16">oil_rand_s16</primary></indexterm><programlisting>#define oil_rand_s16() ((int16_t)(rand()&amp;0xffff))
</programlisting>
<para>
Evaluates to a random integer in the range [-(1&lt;&lt;15), (1&lt;&lt;15)-1].</para>
<para>
</para></refsect2>
