<refsect2 id="oil-rand-s64" role="macro">
<title>oil_rand_s64()</title>
<indexterm zone="oil-rand-s64"><primary sortas="oil_rand_s64">oil_rand_s64</primary></indexterm><programlisting>#define oil_rand_s64() ((int64_t)(oil_rand_s32())&lt;&lt;32 | oil_rand_s32())
</programlisting>
<para>
Evaluates to a random integer in the range [-(1&lt;&lt;63), (1&lt;&lt;63)-1].</para>
<para>
</para></refsect2>
<refsect2 id="oil-rand-u64" role="macro">
<title>oil_rand_u64()</title>
<indexterm zone="oil-rand-u64"><primary sortas="oil_rand_u64">oil_rand_u64</primary></indexterm><programlisting>#define oil_rand_u64() ((uint64_t)(oil_rand_u32())&lt;&lt;32 | oil_rand_u32())
</programlisting>
