<refsect2 id="oil-rand-f32" role="macro">
<title>oil_rand_f32()</title>
<indexterm zone="oil-rand-f32"><primary sortas="oil_rand_f32">oil_rand_f32</primary></indexterm><programlisting>#define oil_rand_f32() (rand()/(RAND_MAX+1.0))
</programlisting>
<para>
Evaluates to a random single-precision floating point number
in the range [0, 1.0).</para>
<para>
</para></refsect2>
<refsect2 id="oil-rand-f64" role="macro">
<title>oil_rand_f64()</title>
<indexterm zone="oil-rand-f64"><primary sortas="oil_rand_f64">oil_rand_f64</primary></indexterm><programlisting>#define oil_rand_f64() (((rand()/(RAND_MAX+1.0))+rand())/(RAND_MAX+1.0))
</programlisting>
<para>
Evaluates to a random double-precision floating point number
in the range [0, 1.0).</para>
<para>
</para></refsect2>
<refsect2 id="oil-random-alpha" role="function">
<title>oil_random_alpha ()</title>
<indexterm zone="oil-random-alpha"><primary sortas="oil_random_alpha">oil_random_alpha</primary></indexterm><programlisting><link linkend="void">void</link>                oil_random_alpha                    (<link linkend="oil-type-u8">oil_type_u8</link> *dest,
